owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The WINGS hasExpandedTemplate is a WINGS workflow object property that represents a connection between a WingsWorkflowExecution having an WingsWorkflowExpandedTemplate.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The WINGS hasPlan is a WINGS workflow object property that represents a connection between a WingsWorkflowExecution having an Workflow Instance.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The WINGS hasStep is a WINGS workflow object property that represents a connection between a WingsWorkflowExecution having an execution step.

owl:ObjectProperty.rdfs:comment: The WINGS hasTemplate is a WINGS workflow object property that represents a connection between a WingsWorkflowExecution having a template.
